  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13063647/vail-colorado-usa-skier-in-vail-2.jpg" alt="intermediatehero" data-udi="umb://media/9824a5b761684fd8ae54fb5d95a9e9d6" /></p>
<h2>Best ski resorts for intermediates</h2>
<p>Are you the skier that enjoys the <a data-udi="umb://document/7da36c04af644ad0b7d6fc820190f5e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7da36c04af644ad0b7d6fc820190f5e5}" title="Insider’s Guide: Where are the best resorts for advanced skiers and snowboarders?">thrill of a black run</a> but also appreciates the <a data-udi="umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1}" title="Ski Holidays for Beginners">comfort of a blue run</a>? </p>
<p>We have selected some of the best <a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">ski resorts</a> designed with intermediate level skiers in mind. Offering the perfect range of the familiarity and ease of greens and blues to build build your confidence, plenty of red runs to give you time to enhance your skills and the odd black when you feel like pushing your ability limits and hoping to go from intermediate to advanced. </p>
<h2>Intermediate ski resorts</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Morzine, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13100856/morzine-500.jpg" alt="morzinefrance" data-udi="umb://media/ba5a0c5857574795b065fdd02ded1a06" /></p>
<p>With modern chairlifts, plenty of wide cruise-ing slopes and the some more challenging ones at <a data-udi="umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55}" title="Insider's Guide: Best High Altitude Ski Resorts">higher altitude</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a> is a great resort for intermediate skiers. The resort itself isn't too big, so it's easy to make you're way around and there are free shuttle buses throughout the town. There are plenty of places to eat and drink, all centered around the towns square.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d}" class="c-btn">View Morzine</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Lech, <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13100858/lech-500.jpg" alt="lechaustria" data-udi="umb://media/3d90082af60943d88260dede35a0e4ea" /></p>
<p>This resort offers high-altitude and <a data-udi="umb://document/b28019985984419899535b05fb4b9b57" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b28019985984419899535b05fb4b9b57}" title="Insider’s Guide: Top 10 snow-sure ski resorts in Europe">snow-sure</a> ski runs, perfect for intermediate skiers that are keen to make the most of everyday, perfecting their downhill turns. Good intermediate skiers can enjoy the well-known White Ring Circuit that links Lech to <a data-udi="umb://document/754fd3eb2ae94fa89ed0dfc04d2b29b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/754fd3eb2ae94fa89ed0dfc04d2b29b6}" title="Zurs">Zurs</a> resort. The town itself is intermate and popular for it's ice bars and champagne offerings. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6}" title="Lech" class="c-btn">View Lech</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Cervinia, <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria"></a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13100859/la-thuile-500.jpg" alt="lathuileitaly" data-udi="umb://media/9da624b280994d8a9ce20f97aded4cce" /></p>
<p>For intermediate skiers, this resort is in the ideal location as it is part of the <a data-udi="umb://document/44c205035969462abff34bd958a9f9af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44c205035969462abff34bd958a9f9af}" title="Aosta Valley Ski Area">Aosta Valley</a>, for days you want to push your skills and also linked with Zermatt so you can cross over to <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. Cervinia offers a good value for money resort with a relaxed <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italian</a> environment. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia" class="c-btn">View Cervinia</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Davos, <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13100863/davos-500.jpg" alt="davosswiss" data-udi="umb://media/4e9cfe5784b34792be3cbadde757ab2a" /></p>
<p>Ideal for intermediates, with 6 skiing areas included in the resort lift pass, meaning a huge variety of runs. This high-altitude resorts has a great mixture of local runs as well, based around the bustling town centre, from which you can take in the surrounding mountain views over a local drink. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df}" class="c-btn">View Davos</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
