<p> </p>
<h2>Intermediate skiers - standout stays</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b94e55ccaa7f460ea0789aa4dc85c0d7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b94e55ccaa7f460ea0789aa4dc85c0d7}" title="Chalet Matine Apartments">Matine Apartments</a></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13080594/62834.jpg" alt="matineapartments" data-udi="umb://media/76d3b49ae5734f049b10aa5f2cab9338" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays"><strong>Ideal for groups.</strong></a> These <a data-udi="umb://document/8ffc82b2f62046538c164fffbcdb7693" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8ffc82b2f62046538c164fffbcdb7693}" title="Apartments (Self-catering)">self-catering apartments</a> are the perfect mix of holiday feel and home like features. With the free use of <a data-udi="umb://document/ff2b50e1829f4726b6cf8c4ab1d52147" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ff2b50e1829f4726b6cf8c4ab1d52147}" title="Hotel Les Champs Fleuris">Hotel Champs Fleuris</a> pool and spa, as well as half-board basis options. These apartments are virtually <a data-udi="umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b}" title="Ski In Ski Out Holidays">ski-in ski-out</a> and opposite the Pleney gondola. The apartments are central to the resort centre, so close to bars and restaurants. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d}" class="c-btn">View Morzine</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2d1a988b56384c33ac863ab4f6295174" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2d1a988b56384c33ac863ab4f6295174}" title="Montana Lodge &amp; Spa Hotel">Montana Lodge</a></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria"></a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13095675/a_8435868_69_70_fused.jpg" alt="montanalodge" data-udi="umb://media/dece5ae5a09b40b38653965379aad67b" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b5cb9765812641b5bc1682861060520d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b5cb9765812641b5bc1682861060520d}" title="Couples Ski Holidays"><strong>Perfect for couples.</strong></a> This cosy, refined lodge with high-quality service and 5 star spa facilities is a dream for relaxing after a busy days skiing. The rooms here are all deluxe and have the finest attention to detail. Providing a free shuttle bus to the ski lifts and back throughout the day, this quality hotel certainly provides a week of <a data-udi="umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46}" title="Ski &amp; Spa Holidays">luxury</a>. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1ab09654d84b4707bd5f8d19918005b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1ab09654d84b4707bd5f8d19918005b5}" class="c-btn">View La Thuile</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3493a2f95f6541acb0cb8d9c332a4aec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3493a2f95f6541acb0cb8d9c332a4aec}" title="Hotel Central Sport">Hotel Central Sport</a></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13073254/central-winter_03.jpg" alt="hotelsport" data-udi="umb://media/1ff4c7e5cbc3483596c407f629b6d4a6" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/43b759307a674eaba22751fc5ef9501a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/43b759307a674eaba22751fc5ef9501a}" title="Single Ski Holidays"><strong>Good for solo skiers.</strong></a> An all round great place to stay while in Davos. With a reputation for good service, appetising food and well decorated bedrooms, this hotel is only a minute from the town centre. It has welcoming and social areas, plus a bar and daily complimentary tea and cake servings. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df}" class="c-btn">View Davos</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e9525dfd1a434205961d8d8184402db1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9525dfd1a434205961d8d8184402db1}" title="Hotel Haldenhof">Hotel Haldenhof</a></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 214.45639187574673px;" src="/media/13050039/austria_arlberg-ski-area_lech_hotel_haldendorf_exterior_night.jpg?width=500&amp;height=214.45639187574673" alt="HotelHaldenhof" data-udi="umb://media/fd89c19f6dd94db1aa587247db044f87" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays"><strong>Good for families.</strong></a> This exclusive hotel is family run and therefore welcomes families to stay. With their unique room offerings, from twins with a sofa bed to superior suites, it can suit most family needs (they can also provide baby monitors on request). Just 2 minutes from the town centre and lifts, but far enough so the towns evenings noise doesn't reach you.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6}" title="Lech" class="c-btn">View Lech</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">More intermediate ski info?</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099564/love-of-first-lifts-520x520.jpg" alt="intermediateskier" data-udi="umb://media/63296d7bc3614fa585d960f0def65027" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ff0b58c00a714f769494f987108454f5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ff0b58c00a714f769494f987108454f5}" title="Insider's Guide: best resorts for intermediates" class="c-btn">Intermediates guide</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Are you a beginner skier?</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099563/love-of-mountains-520x520.jpg" alt="beginnerskier" data-udi="umb://media/ee8a562945d24152bad47b844cba1d9d" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1}" title="Ski Holidays for Beginners" class="c-btn">View skiing for beginners</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Are you an advanced skier?</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099645/love-of-thrill-520x520.jpg" alt="advancedskier" data-udi="umb://media/97de3d4ccd094d81abd0773c51c92704" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb}" title="Skiing for Advanced" class="c-btn">View skiing for advanced</a></p>
</div>
</div>
